:ITN043 :hasManagementAdvice "Use TMP-SMX with caution in elderly patients receiving thiazide diuretics" .
:ITN043 :hasInteractionDescription "In elderly patients concurrently receiving diuretics, mainly thiazide, there appears to be an increased risk of thrombocytopenia with purpura." .

:ITN044 :hasManagementAdvice "Avoid combination or closely monitor CBC for megaloblastic anemia." .
