:ITN096 :hasClinicalEffects "Rare prolongation of prothrombin time." .
:ITN096 :hasInteractionDescription "Concurrent use with amoxicillin." .
:ITN096 :hasManagementAdvice "Undertake appropriate monitoring (e.g., INR)." .

