:ITN271 :hasClinicalEffects "Not Specified" .
:ITN271 :hasInteractionDescription "Trimethoprim has been reported to reduce the renal excretion and increase blood concentrations of zidovudine, zalcitabine, and lamivudine." .
:ITN271 :hasManagementAdvice "Not Specified" .
