:S153 :hasReference :R109 .
:S153 :hasSubstanceDescription "Macrolides are a class of antibiotics that treat a wide range of bacterial infections, including walking pneumonia, whooping cough and strep throat. Commonly prescribed macrolides include azithromycin, clarithromycin, erythromycin, and fidaxomicin." .

