:SP027 :hasReference :R028 .
:SP027 :hasReference :R027 .
:SP027 :hasStewardshipDescription "Complete the full course of Contepo even if you feel better to prevent bacterial resistance. Do not skip doses." .

:SP028 :hasStewardshipDescription "Report any severe side effects or unusual symptoms to your healthcare provider. Kidney and liver function may need monitorng during treatment." .
:SP028 :hasReference :R028 .
:SP028 :hasReference :R027 .

:SP029 :hasStewardshipDescription "May be taken with meals to reduce gastrointestinal discomfort" .
:SP029 :hasReference :R037 .

:SP030 :hasStewardshipDescription "Only use for prescribed bacterial infections (uncomplicated UTIs). Avoid for viral infections." .
